  "instructions": [
    "Place the chopped onions and garlic in a pan, saut\u00e9 until translucent.",
    "Add the finely chopped tomato, salt, cumin, and black peppercorns. Stir well.",
    "Pour in lemon juice and allow to simmer for about 5 minutes.",
    "While sauce is simmering, place black olives on a plate lined with parchment paper or silicone mat.",
    "Drizzle olive oil over the olives evenly and bake at 200\u00b0C for approximately 10-15 minutes until crispy.",
    "Once done, sprinkle chopped tomatoes and onions on top of each crumble to enhance flavors."
